<H1>docker compose files for easy deployment of pihole and unbound.</H1>

<H2>Install Docker</H2>
<br>
<h3>Update and Upgrade>/h3>
    <p>sudo apt update && sudo apt upgrade -y </p>
<br>
<h3>Install Docker</h3>
    <p>curl -fsSL test.docker.com -o get-docker.sh && sh get-docker.sh</p>
<br>
<h3>Add user to Docker Group</h3>
    <p>sudo usermod -aG docker $USER</p>
    <p>sudo reboot now</p>
<br>
<h3>Install Docker-Compose</h3>
    <p>sudo apt-get install libffi-dev libssl-dev</p>
    <p>sudo apt install python3-dev</p>
    <p>sudo apt-get install -y python3 python3-pip</p>
    <p>sudo apt install docker-compose</p>
    <p>sudo systemctl enable docker</p>
<br>
<h3>Deploy Container</h3>
    <b>git clone https://github.com/PadiBo/pihole_unbound_docker-compose.git</b>
    <p>cd pihole_unbound_docker-compose</p>
    <p>docker-compose docker-compose.yml</p>
